1
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:07,680
Mingyue.

2
00:01:26,039 --> 00:01:28,100
She was also poisoned by Wushanxing.

3
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:56,840
Your Highness,

4
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:59,060
His Majesty is expecting you.

5
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:30,640
Ji Mingyue.

6
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:33,050
You better not regret this.

7
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,040
Your Majesty.

8
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,120
Father, you summoned me.

9
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,480
Do you have any orders?

10
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,880
I am old.

11
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:40,280
This world

12
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:43,600
will be yours sooner or later.

13
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,760
Why are you in such a hurry?

14
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,360
Yes.

15
00:03:55,079 --> 00:03:56,920
What are you talking about, Father?

16
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,120
I don't understand.

17
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:02,360
You have been insatiable since childhood.

18
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,440
You are ruthless,

19
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:05,840
but lack wisdom.

20
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,120
I know.

21
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:12,440
You like Ji Mingyue.

22
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,440
But to assassinate me

23
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,880
for her...

24
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,000
You...

25
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,560
You have lost your mind.

26
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:23,320
Father.

27
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,280
Father.

28
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,160
Father,

29
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:26,720
please,

30
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,720
forgive me.

31
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,800
I know I was wrong.

32
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:30,490
Please forgive me, Father.

33
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:33,120
It really was you.

34
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:36,320
You rebelled for a woman.

35
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:40,700
You killed your father and your king.

36
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:43,240
Shen Mingyue must die.

37
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,400
Guards!

38
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:45,240
Guards!

39
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:49,080
Father.

40
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:51,040
As long as you are dead,

41
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,960
the world is mine.

42
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:57,520
How could I rebel?

43
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,880
I just want to tell you

44
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:05,840
that Ji Mingyue must be mine.

45
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:07,680
Must be mine.

46
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:33,480
Mother.

47
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,720
No.

48
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,960
They said Huo Lingyu from the Hanlin Academy

49
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:39,520
was summoned to the palace at the hour of Xu,

50
00:05:39,520 --> 00:05:41,280
and hasn't left yet.

51
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:42,520
Lingyu.

52
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:43,360
Huo Lingyu.

53
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:55,650
The Wushanxing poison was cured with her.

54
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,480
But the Qianji poison...

55
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,040
Jiuying.

56
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:13,280
The one-month deadline has arrived.

57
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:15,140
You still haven't got the ledger.

58
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,760
This time, the antidote

59
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:18,200
is only half a pill.

60
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:29,280
The antidote comes once a month.

61
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:31,600
I can neither recover nor die.

62
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:36,300
I wonder how much longer I'll be controlled by this Qianji poison.

63
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,360
I am incompetent.

64
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:47,280
I didn't realize there was a problem with the incense burner.

65
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,140
Your Highness.

66
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:51,940
Perhaps we should have the imperial physician take a look.

67
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,400
You ran fast.

68
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:02,280
You'd better not let me find out who you are.

69
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:03,530
Where is Huo Lingyu?

70
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:06,520
I couldn't find you last night.

71
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:08,520
So I escorted Lord Huo out of the palace first.

72
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:12,120
Right now, he is in the side hall study teaching the Ninth Prince.

73
00:07:25,080 --> 00:07:26,320
Tracing

74
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:28,050
doesn't mean copying rigidly.

75
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:30,160
Relax your wrist.

76
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:31,960
Write decisively.

77
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:34,100
Control your strokes.

78
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,960
And follow your heart.

79
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,600
It's a promise.

80
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,680
Today at dusk,

81
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,440
when the moon rises above the willows,

82
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:54,040
wait for me at Wangyue Bridge.

83
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:56,500
I have something very important to tell you.

84
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,840
Miss Shen, this meeting is inappropriate.

85
00:07:58,840 --> 00:07:59,920
Today is Qixi.

86
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:00,960
Meeting today

87
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:02,240
might harm your reputation, Miss Shen.

88
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,240
Cut the nonsense.

89
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,840
If I tell you to go, you go.

90
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,600
If you dare not to show up,

91
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:08,560
I'll go to the Huo Residence to find you myself.

92
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:09,240
You

93
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,240
know me.

94
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,680
I always keep my word.

95
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:21,480
Alright.

96
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:43,400
By the grace of Heaven, the Emperor decrees:

97
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,680
Shen Mingyue

98
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:46,040
is pure and noble,

99
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:47,400
gentle and virtuous.

100
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:48,920
She has my heart.

101
00:08:48,920 --> 00:08:50,760
The position of Empress is vacant,

102
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:52,720
and I wish to make her my Empress.

103
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:55,120
He is as bright as the moon among the clouds.

104
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:56,560
But I...

105
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:58,680
It's fine.

106
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,440
Let it be.

107
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:39,260
I pay my respects to Her Majesty the Empress. My respects, Mother.

108
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:43,520
The Huo family is involved in the gold embezzlement case.

109
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:44,850
Should I tell him first?

110
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:46,200
Huo Lingyu.

111
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,480
Where were you last night?

112
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:50,560
Her Majesty summoned me,

113
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:52,620
so naturally, I was in Fengyi Palace.

114
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,280
Huo Lingyu.

115
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,000
Arrest him.

116
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:00,560
Yes.

117
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:07,840
The Huo clan colluded with the frontier official Baili Jinghong.

118
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:08,960
They secretly cooked the books,

119
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:09,960
and embezzled gold.

120
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,280
The entire clan will be punished.

121
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:12,000
Shackle him.

122
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:12,680
Wait.

123
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,880
I am an imperial scholar.

124
00:10:15,160 --> 00:10:16,680
Before the three judicial departments convict him,

125
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:18,410
he doesn't have to be shackled.

126
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:19,920
Mother.

127
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:21,730
He is your man after all.

128
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:23,840
Aren't you going to plead for him

129
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:24,900
or worry about him?

130
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:27,730
Why should I be worried?

131
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:30,320
Then in your opinion, Mother,

132
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,480
how should the Huo clan

133
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,800
be dealt with?

134
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,810
If the charges are true,

135
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:38,720
Naturally, the whole family will be executed.

136
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,040
Oh.

137
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,960
Isn't this Ninth Brother?

138
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:53,960
You didn't even say a word when you saw me.

139
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,490
Greetings, Your Highness.

140
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,400
Ninth Brother.

141
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:04,800
Your teacher broke the law and corrupted the imperial court.

142
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:07,800
Don't follow his example.

143
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:09,120
I wouldn't dare.

144
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:22,400
Strange.

145
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:24,480
That dog emperor isn't dead yet.

146
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:26,280
How dare he touch the Huo family?

147
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:32,080
This is the sound of national mourning.

148
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:33,490
Father has passed away.

149
00:11:43,280 --> 00:11:47,040
Your Majesty the Empress, please receive the edict.

150
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:55,120
By the grace of Heaven,

151
00:11:55,280 --> 00:11:56,800
the Emperor decrees:

152
00:11:57,280 --> 00:12:00,560
I have been the emperor for over twenty years.

153
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:02,600
Grateful for Empress Ji's

154
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:05,200
deep love, though we cannot grow old together,

155
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,560
I cannot bear to leave her behind.

156
00:12:06,560 --> 00:12:07,800
After I pass away,

157
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:10,720
I grant the Empress to be buried with me in the same tomb.

158
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:12,000
Respect this.

159
00:12:13,920 --> 00:12:15,760
Please receive the edict.

160
00:12:24,680 --> 00:12:26,740
Commit suicide to be buried with him?

161
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:28,380
Does he deserve it?

162
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:31,560
My Shen family has slaved for the Ji clan for three generations.

163
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:33,640
Any favors we owed have long been repaid.

164
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:36,520
He is delusional to think I would be buried with him.

165
00:12:37,280 --> 00:12:40,340
He claimed I love eating exotic fish from the South Sea,

166
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:42,900
exhausting 300 horses to death every month.

167
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:45,600
In fact, he just heard this fish could prolong life

168
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:47,200
and wanted to eat it himself.

169
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:48,960
To seek immortality,

170
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:50,840
he extracted hearts to make medicine.

171
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:53,880
He used the excuse that I wanted to refine an elixir of youth.

172
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:55,640
He slung mud at me while alive,

173
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,800
and won't let me go even in death.

174
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:02,200
Your Highness, please make preparations for the aftermath early.

175
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:04,660
Follow the decree and join the late emperor.

176
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:07,340
What if I refuse to accept the decree?

177
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:10,360
I know Your Highness has great power.

178
00:13:11,160 --> 00:13:12,960
If you disobey the emperor's will

179
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:14,440
and openly resist the decree,

180
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:18,880
no one in the Shen family will be spared.
